body: sure a group of us would harvest mushrooms which grew in our area and brew it into tea which we would drink like i said the first few times were incredible a sense of unity among the group and some really fun times exploring the nearby forest the nights seemed to last forever and we just had so much fun as time went on we started to push the boundaries a little more at first we were all only having a couple of cups of tea and some weed but after a few times our confidence and bravery grew and we started having more and more cups each time the night of my bad trip i think i had about 7 8 cups we were sitting around in a living room and the shrooms kicked in for me but not them which gave me immediate anxiety i started to get worried that that something was wrong why was it working for me and not them the walls were moving shapes were forming colours became really vivid and intense shadows moving everywhere i looked and although that was quite pleasant i remember my friends staring at me like something was wrong i panicked i went outside to get some air and was staring into an open paddock i convinced myself that i had been drugged by my friends and they were about to do something horrible to me i did not know what to do so i ran through the paddock i just ran after several minutes of running the shrooms had fully kicked in i suddenly had no idea where i was and no memory of why i was running and i was alone in a forest area near where we lived i could not remember being in the living room taking shrooms with friends just moments before i did not know why i was so fucked up and i could not trace the chain of events in my mind i had no memories at all things began to get really scary from this point on i was hearing noises and seeing strange shapes and figures in the forest i kept walking hiding behind things and trying to remember what the fuck i was doing nothing was coming to me the wave of the shroom trip kept coming getting more and more intense i was alone i was utterly terrified i was seeing ghosts walking through the forest i thought it was snowing in the middle of australian summer i saw a large monster there were evil faces in the stars the wind was talking to me i was tripping hard then the worst thing happened i realized i had no recollection of anything at all from my life and i panicked that i was going mad and would stay this way forever then i finally remembered i went to my friends house and we drank some tea now i am fucked i remember going over this 100 times in my mind i could not get past that train of thought an hour or so past when i was found stumbling around near my apartment by a girl who also lived in the same block she walked me and thought i was just drunk as i was making no sense and staggering around i got inside my apartment and it was like i was looking at everything in it for the very first time i did not recognise this place i did not recognise the photos on the wall i refused to believe this was my life home i was really confused i was laying on the bed still trying to remember anything the lamp on my desk used to make strange shadows on the ceiling the shadows were moving with the shroom trip they formed a face on the ceiling it slightly protruded from the roof and yelled something at me i crawled underneath the bed terrified then there was a knock at the door the girl who had walked me home had called my girlfriend at the time i opened the door but again it was like looking at someone for the first time i did not know who it was and told her to go away i later learned that my friends i took the shrooms with had already called her when i ran away and so had the other girl she knew what was happening and forced her way into the apartment i remember her just hugging me on the bed for hours and nursing me to sleep i was in and out of sleep for a few hours when suddenly as if someone flicked a switch it was all over i sat up on the bed everything was normal again i knew exactly where i was who i was what had happened and everything from before it was like i took a dip into complete madness my mind went to places i had never considered before i stared into something very very dark it was the scariest experience of my life and somewhere i never want to go again i have stayed away from drugs since still have the odd toke though i feel the whole experience has somewhat damaged me psychologically and i have never truly been the same since it brought on a fear in me which never existed before even 15 years on i still think back to the night and seemed so real
